messages.text: Hi, I need help with my order.
Sure, I can help with that. Can you provide your order number?
Can I return an item?
Yes, of course. Do you have the receipt?
I do. Here it is.
The app is crashing.
I'm sorry to hear that. Can you tell me what you were doing when it crashed?
Is the discount still available?
Let me check that for you.
Yes, it's still available until the end of the month.
How can I update my address?
You can update it from your profile settings in the app.
I received the wrong item.
I'm sorry for the inconvenience. We will send you the correct item right away.
What payment methods do you accept?
We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and Apple Pay.
Do you ship internationally?
Yes, we ship to most countries. Shipping fees vary based on the destination.
Can I change my order after placing it?
You can make changes to your order within 24 hours of placement.
The website is not loading.
Please try clearing your browser's cache and cookies.
